thread.title_full: Solid Apollo LED reviewed by William

author: William
title: William
text: Aluminum channels, diffuser screens, end caps, dimmer switches, and power supply worked perfectly and looks great. Everyone who comes into the kitchen wants to know what are the funny looking plates. Onnce they see how the dimmer switch turns the led strip light on and off and can dim or brighten the led strip with a touch of the finger, they are very impressed.
